Package com.ibm.team.process.common

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAccessGroup
    An access group represents a group of items that are used as a context to provide read access to one or more items.
    IAccessGroupHandle
    Handle to an IAccessGroup.
    IAccessGroupMember
    Represents a member of an access group which includes an item and a descriptor for the context in which the item is contained in the group.
    IAddElement
    Represents the add-element child of a configuration-data-delta element.
    IAddition
    Represents the addition child of an add-element within a configuration-data-delta element.
    IBehaviorConfiguration
    A behavior configuration represents the behavior specified in the process specification/customization for a specific operation.
    IConfigurationDataDeltaElement
    Represents a configuration-data-delta process specification XML element.
    IDescription
    A description of an element.
    IDevelopmentLine
    A project area development line.
    IDevelopmentLineConfiguration
    Representation of an configuration of a development line.
    IDevelopmentLineHandle
    Handle to an IDevelopmentLine.
    IDevelopmentLineState
    Represents the initial state of a development line as defined by a process definition.
    IItemChangeReport
    An item change report reifies modifications to a set of items in the course of the execution of an operation.
    IIteration
    An iteration in a project area.
    IIterationConfiguration
    Representation of a configuration of an iteration.
    IIterationHandle
    Handle to an IIteration.
    IIterationState
    Represents the initial state of an iteration as defined by a process definition.
    IIterationType
    A type of iteration.
    IIterationTypeHandle
    Handle to an IIterationType.
    IModifyElement
    Represents the modify-element child of a configuration-data-delta element.
    INamed
    A mix-in interface for elements that have a name and a description associated with them.
    IProcessArea
    Common interface for project and team areas.
    IProcessAreaHandle
    Handle to an IProcessArea.
    IProcessAttachment
    A process attachment allows content to be associated with a process container at a path which is specified relative to the container.
    IProcessAttachmentHandle  
    IProcessConfigurationData  
    IProcessConfigurationElement
    A process configuration element is a node in a tree of element.
    IProcessContainer
    A mix-in interface for process items that contain process data.
    IProcessContainerHandle  
    IProcessDefinition
    A process definition consists of the process id the definition of the process details the schema of the settings the process supports the list of process domains belonging to this process As the set of item types and platform operations is extensible, the activities and resources governed by a process are extensible.
    IProcessDefinitionHandle  
    IProcessItem
    Supertype for all auditable items introduced by the team process support.
    IProcessItemHandle  
    IProcessStateModel
    A model representing the current state of an IProcessContainer
    IProjectArea
    A project area is owned by a project team and contains or references all artifacts and all relationships between these artifacts that constitute the resources of a development project.
    IProjectAreaHandle  
    IProjectLink
    A project link.

    IReadAccessList

    IRole2
